HEADWORD: Birdbolt
<hw>Bird"bolt`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A short blunt
arrow for killing birds without piercing them.</def>
<specif>Hence:</specif> <def>Anything which smites without
penetrating.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

